{"tid":2034914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"立法會預留30小時審議國歌法　料下周四完成","createTime":"2020-05-25T14:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T17:06:31.000Z","uid":153689,"like":31,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"09d9def0e01e300c8a59c90e8c339c26dddd1b86","tid":2034914,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】《國歌條例草案》周三立法會大會恢復二讀，主席梁君彥已預留約30小時審議，預計下周四完成。<br />\n<br />\n立法會外一帶加強布防，被大量水馬圍封至中信大廈外一段龍匯道，出入口有警員駐守。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥指已決定，就所有條文及修正案，進行合併辯論，並預留四日共30小時處理，預計下星期四完成審議及表決。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，由於修正案內容不可改變國歌法基本原則，只可更改國歌法在香港實施的細節，因此由12名民主派議員提交共49項修正案，最終只批出22項，包括由陳志全提出要求教育學生國歌作曲及作詞人生平及死因。"},{"pid":"f8a7568320115e90b4ebddae1d98173c6de25636","tid":2034914,"uid":153689,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392204&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3mHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=05c3fe56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392204&h=335ad446\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392204</a>"},{"pid":"08f3d141628309b3ec5a98e45321040e4f0d4256","tid":2034914,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbd7e4ae97cd2951de32ed5bcf41a3cc674f4f4a","tid":2034914,"uid":2054,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"六四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9192b7cb288addb400308d157e5ab7d0b759c42f","tid":2034914,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"626038bd5103165aa9738db1d36aad53175ccfb3","tid":2034914,"uid":153689,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bbd7e4ae97cd2951